Pathway explored : REACTOME POSTMITOTIC NUCLEAR PORE COMPLEX NPC REFORMATION

This pathway contain 27 genes.

In these 27 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.
